title: Bankruptcy Auction of 2022 Isuzu NQR Flatbed Truck
last_item_closes_display: Thursday, Sep 4, 2025 between 10:00 AM and 10:07 AM
intro: Due to bankruptcy, this ultra-low-mileage 2022 Isuzu NQR Flatbed Truck is up for auction! View our extensive photo gallery, or come to the scheduled public inspection and view this truck in person. Bidding starts at just $5!
